      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sausages and veg are cooking, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>onion marmalade </strong>in 100ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>onion gravy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
