    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausages have browned and the veg is tender, pour your <strong>onion gravy stock </strong>evenly over the top</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 5 min – this is your <strong>sausage & roasted veg tray bake</strong></p>",
